metadata.name: TinyBox #1
metadata.description:
TinyBox 1 of 202 in Phase 1 TinyBoxes is to Autoglyphs as Avastars is to CryptoPunks. TinyBoxes are animated patterns of shapes and colors generated and rendered 100% on-chain. Innovative features of TinyBoxes include dynamic rendering settings, 24 animations, and 11 exclusive color schemes released in phases. 
Our contract has been designed as efficiently as possible, with a minting fee of just 260k gas. TinyBoxes gives back to its community; giving back 50% of gas spent as referral rewards, prizes and giveaways.
